Okay.  <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Major</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> clarification.<br>
<br>
First off.  <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong> What happened between Amae and Apep, PoAmae and PoApep, has <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>little</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> to do with my leaving EQ.</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
